descriptionHtml:
Resources: archive from UNPB and Osare Swimsuit - UNP

Require:
Skeleton that support TBBP (e.g XPMS or custom skeleton replacer)

Installation:
1. Install [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/15216/]Osare Swimsuit - UNP[/url]
2. Unpack the contents to your Skyrim data folder.
3. Overwrite files

Location:
Qasmoke(testing hall)
1 - [coc qasmoke] in the console.
2 - Buy it by merchant
3 - [coc Riverwood] in the console.

Credit: anano
author: anano
